~ start
do GameDialogueManager.change_emote_color.emit(Vector4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 1.0), Vector4(119.0/255.0, 119.0/255.0, 119.0/255.0, 1.0))
do change_emote_visibility.emit(true)
if !guide_met
	Daniel: [[Hi|Hello|Howdy]], I am Daniel, your helper guide.
	Daniel: It is nice to meet you.
	Daniel: Welcome to your new farm.
	set ToolManager.tools_enabled = false
	set guide_met = true
Daniel: As you can see the cows and chickens are hungry.
Daniel: You need to grow some crops to feed them.
if !ToolManager.tools_enabled:
	Daniel: Here are some seeds to grow some crops.
	- OK, thanks for the seeds
		do ToolManager.enable_tool_buttons()
		Daniel: You are welcome, now you are ready to grow your own farm.
	- No, I don't want them
		Daniel: As you wish, return to me when you're ready.
do interactable_label_component.show()
=> END